"Social media users are discussing rumors regarding Vladimir Putin's absence, with hashtags #putinmissing and #putindead trending. Posts claim Putin has not appeared in public for two to three weeks, noting he looked \"pale and unsteady\" during his last appearance. While some users question his status, others suggest the Kremlin is preparing for St. Patrick's Day or provide evidence of his presence to counter the rumors. The official narrative states that Putin is fine."